window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>He's rough around the edges, a sweet talker with a protective heart. Johnny works his Southern charm under my skin despite my best efforts to resist him. He's my best friend, my other half. He says he loves me until one decision alters our lives forever. The damage is irreparable. Johnny's sorrow runs deep. He takes his pain out on his friends and pushes me into the arms of someone who does more harm than goodâ€”then disappears without a word.</p> <p>When he returns, he wants me back, but it's complicated.</p> <p>I'm pregnant. And I don't know if the baby is his.</p>"; 
